Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.55,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫富樫樟叶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我哥哥 富樫勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是初中2年级 稍微有点怪的时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥晚饭要凉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我dark flame master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在进行身心的修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了集中精神 也必须要远离一切食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要进行6小时的冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这期间 不能与任何人进行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦叶也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥想啊 冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要聚集暗之魂魄才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是在学校里流行的那个「决斗」什么的卡片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人没问题的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 让你哥陪你去吧
