Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮出来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你月亮出来了没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就用这个了…
