Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉 就在附近 隐藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 樟叶酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 美香酱 你这是要去哪里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去下文具店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹… 难道那是樟叶酱的哥哥？
