Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香酱？ 美香酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说我家的哥哥其实很帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我是这么想的
