Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北欧雷神之锤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我安静一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太 解放暗之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样 我们每天都尽情地闹在一起
